name: Konferensie Saterdag Oggen Past Jan
chorusText:
DIE GEMEENTE BRING AAN U DIE LOF:	B-mol

Die gemeente bring aan U die lof
Die eer en heerlikheid
Die gemeente bring aan U die lof
Die eer en heerlikheid
Net aan U - lof en eer (2 x)
Die gemeente bring aan U die lof
Die eer en heerlikheid.
Kom sing ‘n nuwe lied virHom
kom sing ‘n nuwe lied vir Jesus
kom bring die lof en dank aanHom
Want Hy’s die Koningwatweerkom

Kom sing ‘n nuwe lied uitjou hart
LaatjouleweHombesing
Want Hy is die Koning, Hy is die Here
Sing ‘n nuwe lied virHom
Ek is verlos o prys U Naam
ere ereaan die Lam
net aan U gee ek my oor
ek is verlos, jaek is verlos
Wonderful, wonderful Jesus is to me, 
Counselor, mighty God, Prince of peace is He
Saving me, keeping me, from all sin and shame 
Wonderful is my Redeemer, praise His Name

Wondervol, wondervol is my Jesus my
Wyse Raad, Sterke God, Vredevors is Hy
Hy lei my, Hymaak my vry
Van my sondelas
Wodervol is my Verlosser, prysSyNaam
We are standing on Holy ground

 We are standing on Holy ground
and I know that there 
are angels all around
Let’s  just praise Jesus now
for we are standing in His presence
on Holy ground
There’s a precious hiding place
In Jesus Name, in Jesus Name
There’s a cleft of heavenly grace
In Jesus side, in Jesus side
There’s a shelter from all sin
from all fear, from all shame
All the world may enter in
a precious place in Jesus Name
